# BS_Def64.sys ![:inline](/images/twitter_verified.png) 

### Description

BS_Def64.sys is a vulnerable driver and more information will be added as found.
- **UUID**: 4a80da66-f8f1-4af9-ba56-696cfe6c1e10
- **Created**: 2023-01-09
- **Author**: Michael Haag
- **Acknowledgement**:  | [](https://twitter.com/)

{{< button "https://github.com/magicsword-io/LOLDrivers/raw/main/drivers/8abbb12e61045984eda19e2dc77b235e.bin" "Download" >}}{{< button "https://www.magicsword.io/premium" "Block" "red" >}}
{{< tip "warning" >}}
This download link contains the vulnerable driver!

{{< /tip >}}

### Commands

```
sc.exe create BS_Def64.sys binPath=C:\windows\temp\BS_Def64.sys type=kernel &amp;&amp; sc.exe start BS_Def64.sys
```


| Use Case | Privileges | Operating System | 
|:---- | ---- | ---- |
| Elevate privileges | kernel | Windows 10 |
